
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-irtf-sam-hybrid-overlay-framework-02.txt'>
    <title>"Hybrid Overlay Multicast Framework", John Buford</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-irtf-sam-hybrid-overlay-framework-02.txt</link>
    <description>We describe an experimental framework for constructing SAM sessions using hybrid combinations of Application Layer Multicast, native multicast, and multicast tunnels.  We leverage AMT relay and gateway elements for interoperation between native regions and ALM regions. The framework allows different overlay algorithms and different ALM control algorithms to be used.</description>
    <dc:date>2008-02-25T08:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
